			<h2><a href='redline-@BUILD_VERSION@/index.html'>Redline</a></h2>
			<p>Redline is a pure Java library for manipulating <a href='http://www.rpm.org'>RPM Package Manager</a> packages. Currently the project supports reading and creating packages and has an included <a href='http://ant.apache.org'>Ant</a> task useful for integration with build systems. Support for package signatures will be added in a future release.</p>
